text.section:
In accordance with the provisions of this subtitle and the authorizing resolution, all bonds of the same issue:
Subject to the prior and superior rights of outstanding bonds, claims, or obligations, may have a prior and paramount lien on the revenue of the sewerage facility, over and ahead of:
All bonds of any subsequent issue payable from the revenue;
Any claims of any nature subsequently arising against the revenue; and
Any obligations of any nature subsequently incurred against the revenue;
May be equally and ratably secured by a lien on the revenue, without priority because of:
Number;
Date of bonds;
Date of sale;
Date of execution; or
Date of delivery; and
In the manner and to the extent set forth in the authorizing resolution, including a provision for the subordination of fewer than all the bonds, may be subordinated and junior in standing, with respect to the payment of principal and interest and the security for the payment, to any other bonds that the authorizing resolution designates.
